yingyinNormal.en: Every street corner it seems, is familiar through documentary, movie and song.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每一个街角都是纪录片、电影和歌曲的灵感，并且因而被人熟识。

yingyinNormal.en: Ross, we actually watched the documentary together. Ooh. My Chinese food. Let me get my cash.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们是一起看那部纪录片的，我的外卖来了，我去拿钱。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, that documentary last night was actually better than I thought it would be. Really?
yingyinNormal.zh: 昨晚那部纪录片其实比我想象中要来的好看呢。真的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: This is a documentary about Mr. Spock. I'm sure if there's nudity, it will be tasteful.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是关于史巴克先生的纪录片，就算真有裸露镜头，也一定很有品味。

yingyinNormal.en: See, see. Look at my Netflix queue. There's two documentaries and the movie Friends with Benefits, which I thought was a documentary about employer health care plans.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看我的线上视频待看列表。两部纪录片还有电影《朋友也上床》[朋友有福利]，我本来以为这也是纪录片讲雇主提供健康保险。

yingyinNormal.en: Really? You would have slept with me after a three hour documentary on dams? No. No woman would.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是吗？你要是看了三小时水坝的纪录片 你还有性致吗？没有，没女人会有。

yingyinNormal.en: Leonard Nimoy's son is working on a documentary that he started with his father before he passed away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 伦纳德·尼莫伊的儿子在拍一部纪录片，在他爸爸过世前就开始拍摄了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yeah, sure. There's also an amazing documentary about building a dam on a river in South America.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，没错，不过还有一场精彩的纪录片讲述在南美洲的一条河上建一座水坝。
